Careers







Careers / Jobs in the U.S.






Jobs in the U.S.

CB&I is a multinational, multicultural company with competitive compensation and benefits.
We are currently seeking professionals for North American positions in Engineering, Technology, Project Management and Consultancy, Administration, Accounting/Finance, Human Resources, IT, Legal and Sales.
We're also looking for skilled trades, field non-manual and field supervisory personnel.



Professional
CB&I is seeking professionals for North American positions across multiple disciplines.



Craft and Field Supervision
CB&I is currently looking for skilled trades, including welders, pipefitters, electricians, boilermakers, fitters, carpenters, painters and more at project sites, fabrication shops, warehouses and operating plants. We are also seeking experienced field supervisors.



U.S. Military Veterans
CB&I is a military-friendly supporter of soldiers, veterans and their spouses. We are actively seeking employees who have served in the United States Armed Forces.



MOX Project
CB&I is seeking employees for jobs on the MOX Project, a Mixed Oxide (MOX) Fuel Fabrication Facility we are designing and building at the U.S. Department of Energy's Savannah River Site in South Carolina.




(2017 EEO Policy Statement)







