Professional
Craft and Field Supervision
U.S. Military Veterans
CB&I Federal Services
MOX Project

Jobs Outside the U.S.

Professional

Students and Recent Graduates

Students and Recent Graduates

Why CB&I?

Leader in the global energy infrastructure market
Worldwide locations and international opportunities
Growing end markets and strong backlog of work
Industry-leading safety performance
Military-friendly employer
Focus on career development
Collaborative and inclusive culture

Recruiting Scams
Criminal elements around the globe are using the CB&I name and logo in emails to solicit personal information and monetary fees from applicants. 
                                                                  
Please be aware that CB&I does not charge candidates a fee for employment. CB&I will never ask for money as part of the application process. Additionally, all personal information sought from applicants is via our online careers portal, which applicants access on their own.
  
If you have questions about the legitimacy of a recruitment email purporting to come from CB&I, please contact us by telephone at +1 225 987 6215.











