Company Summary
Chicago Bridge & Iron Company N.V. designs, builds, repairs and modifies steel tanks and other steel plate structures and associated systems.  The Company designs and builds petroleum terminals, refinery pressure vessels, low temperature and cryogenic storage facilities and elevated water storage tanks for clients internationally.   





 






















